{"word":"ἐμπάσσω","slug":"ἐμπάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπάσσω</b></el> <el>(attic <el>-ττω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πάσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><i>to sprinkle in</i> or <i>on</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to weave</i> as patterns <i>in</i> a web of cloth, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}